scriptCommands.description: Starts DND via DND Me. The parameter has to be a menu item or slider equivalent: 15m, 30m, 1h, 2h, ..., 12h, next, next-hour, next-half-hour; it defaults to next. next-hour means the next 60m mark, next-half-hour means the next 30m mark and next means the first of the two. For example, if it's 9:22, next-hour means 10:00, next-half-hour means 9:30 and next means 9:30.
scriptCommands.title: Start DND
